<article class="speakerslist jumbotron d-none d-sm-block">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <% topSpeakers.forEach(function(speaker) {%>
                <div class="col-md text-center">
                    <h4 class="speakerslist-title">
                        <%=speaker.title%>
                    </h4>
                    <div class="speakerslist-name">
                        with
                        <a href="/dogs/<%=speaker.shortname%>">
                            <%=speaker.name%>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                    <p class="speakerslist-info mt-2">
                        <a href="/dogs/<%=speaker.shortname%>">
                            <img class="speakerslist-img rounded-circle" src="/images/dogs/<%=speaker.shortname%>.jpg"
                                alt="Photo of <%=speaker.name%>" />
                        </a>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <%})%>
        </div>
    </div>
</article>

<div class="container mt-4">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-8">
            <article class="article maincontent">
                <h1>Who are we?</h1>
                <p>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-bone"></i> Paws & Claws is a (fictional) non-profit organization of
                    dog-loving professionals who are determined to make our world better for our canine friends.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Being informed is the very best tip we can offer when it comes to making a conscientious
                    decision as a potential volunteer. Before jumping paws-first into your new position, it's
                    important to consider the type of animal shelter that best fits your tolerances
                    and personality. Oh, and remember to be honest with yourself.
                </p>
            </article>
            <article class="article maincontent">
                <h2 class="article-title">Get Busy!</h2>
                <p>
                    Get out there and volunteer at your <a
                        href="https://www.aspca.org/adopt-pet/adoptable-dogs-your-local-shelter">local shelter</a>,
                    <a href="https://www.aspcapro.org/sites/default/files/seattle-animal-shelter-foster-1.pdf">or
                        you could try
                        fostering</a>, or take your dog to
                    <a href="https://www.bringfido.com/sitemap/attraction/">a local dog park</a>. If you&apos;re in
                    FaceBook, you can also
                    <a href="https://www.facebook.com/AmericanKennelClub/groups">join
                        the AKC FaceBook group</a>.
                </p>
            </article>
        </div>

        <aside class="col-md-4">
            <article class="sidebar">
                <h1 class="sidebar-title">Who should come?</h1>
                <ul class="sidebar-body">
                    <li>Are you interested in supporting and volunteering at local shelters?</li>
                    <li>Are you obsessed with and adore man's best friend?</li>
                    <li>
                        Spend countless hours checking out cute dog vids online?
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </article>

        </aside>
    </div>
</div>

